Title: China, Myanmar jostle over Myitsone project during Suu Kyi’s visit
Content: The stalled Myitsone dam project — widely seen as a litmus test of a new phase of ties with China — came under sharp focus on Thursday during talks between the visiting leader of Myanmar Aung San Suu
Author: Atul Aneja
